сущности:
photo
post
comment
hashtag
user

эндпоинты:
GET /api/photo
GET /api/photo/{photo_id}
PUT /api/photos/{photo_id}
DELETE /api/photo/{photo_id}


GET /api/post
GET /api/post/{post_id}
PUT /api/post/{photo_id}
DELETE /api/post/{photo_id}


GET /api/comment/{post_id}
POST /api/comment/{post_id}
PUT /api/comment/{post_id}/{user_id}
DELETE /api/comment/{post_id}


GET /api/hashtag?size=20&page=1
GET /api/hashtag/{hashtag_name}


GET /api/user
GET /api/user/{user_id}
PUT /api/user/{user_id}
DELETE /api/user/{user_id}


POST /api/signup
POST /api/signin